sentence: They include the N-terminal scaffold attachment factor -A / B, acinus and PIAS (SAP) domain, the Proline - Isoleucine - Asparagine -Ile- Threonine (PINIT) motif, the RING finger domain - Zinc finger -like zinc -binding domain (RLD), the highly acidic domain (AD), the SUMO-interacting motif (SIM), and the serine / threonine -rich C-terminal region (S / T).
